        "description": "The Presence is a proof-of-concept demonstration showing how interactive elements can make 360° films more immersive. The story follows four characters through a séance gone wrong. This demo contains two new approaches to VR storytelling: \"active\" and \"reactive.\" In both versions, the viewer influences how the story unfolds. In the \"active\" version the viewer is able to jump between multiple perspectives at will; while in the \"reactive\" version the viewer's gaze motivates the next shot, editing the film organically.\n\n          Additional storage required:  ~1.5GB\n          Runtime:  ~6 minutes\n\nThe Presence contains strong language and violence and is recommended for a mature audience only.\n\nThe Presence works with the Gear VR touchpad or most Bluetooth controllers. For viewers who have a SubPac, The Presence utilizes SubPac’s tactile audio technology for a more immersive experience.",
